FEATURES
========

Falls and their resulting injuries have become a serious public health 
issue among older adults. 
http://www.intelihealth.com/IH/ihtIH/WSIHW000/22030/23724/353819.html?d=dmtContent

Hearing tests can determine if you have hearing loss and can help to 
identify the cause. Your doctor can then explain treatment options.
http://www.intelihealth.com/IH/ihtIH/WSIHW000/22030/23724/353487.html?d=dmtContent

Compared to young and middle-age adults, people over 70 are more likely
to be involved in a crash while driving and more likely to die in that 
crash. 
http://www.intelihealth.com/IH/ihtIH/WSIHW000/22030/22031/311060.html?d=dmtContent

